headMarkup:
<style>
    .jumbotron {
        background: url(/sfsites/c/resource/coralcloudsite/jumbotron.jpeg) no-repeat;
        background-position: center;
        background-size: cover;
        min-height:350px;
        color:#FFFFFF;
    }
</style>

<script>
    var contactId;
    window.addEventListener('userInfo', e => {
        console.log("userInfo received, saving contactId: "+ e.detail.contactId);
        contactId = e.detail.contactId;
    });
    window.addEventListener("onEmbeddedMessagingReady", e => {
        embeddedservice_bootstrap?.prechatAPI?.setHiddenPrechatFields({
            "Customer_ID": contactId
    });
});
</script>
label: main
